object.name: text
object.text: Amelia? ... So it's too late. You're one of them now. I was hoping we... I wouldn't have to-

object.name: text
object.text: Why are you doing this to us? Did Da-... Did Father make you do this?!

object.name: text
object.text: We must take this land or our people will starve to death! Turn around and I'll let you go.

object.name: text
object.text:
NO! I won't let anyone get hurt anymore!
Let me go talk to him!

object.name: text
object.text:
You know I can't do that.
I'm sorry...Amelia...
